{"id":233995,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/共识网-每天/","date":"2012-06-22T14:46:18Z","modified":"2012-06-22T14:46:18Z","title":"共识网 | 每天","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<p><img class=\"c2\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/120622/2243221D8-0.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>               <strong>每天</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    每天辛苦同样的繁重</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    托举起城市日渐的灿烂</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    每天都是同样的疲惫</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    夜深人静后总是难以入眠的相思</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    当思念成为一种常态</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    生存的艰辛依旧蔓延日后岁月</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    农民工的旅途</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    只能是候鸟般地不断迁徙</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    看那城市浮华的背后</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    只能是农民工无奈的落寞</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    霓虹之下的驻足</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    常是被烟酒吞噬的孤独</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    此时每天的渴望</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    就是让那日月如梭</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    渴盼春节短暂的团聚</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    来重温一年难得的温馨</strong></p>\n<p><strong>      <img class=\"c2\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.21ccom.net/uploads/allimg/120622/2243221153-1.jpg\" /></strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/14df7b52EKCgBk8MZdE.gif.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/72b7593e2243221D8-0.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}